    kind: note
    message: No visible change to `schemas_frontmatter/Cargo.toml`, though the prompt requires it.
    reasoning: The prompt requires creating `schemas_frontmatter/Cargo.toml` with package name `schemas_frontmatter` as part of this module. Only `schemas_frontmatter/src/lib.rs` appears in the recorded changes. The agent's final message claims the whole workspace builds and tests pass ('cargo test' green, 13 tests), which is only possible if a valid Cargo.toml exists, so it was presumably created or already present but not captured in the diff shown here.
